trans-unit.source: Enumerates the resources in a binary resources (.resources) file by reading sequential resource name/value pairs.
trans-unit.target: Nummererer ressurser i en binær ressursfilen (.resources) ved å lese sekvensielle ressursen navn/verdi-par.

trans-unit.source: **Security Note**: Calling methods in this class with untrusted data is a security risk.
trans-unit.target: **Obs!**: kaller metoder i denne klassen med uklarerte data er en sikkerhetsrisiko.

trans-unit.source: Call the methods in the class only with trusted data.
trans-unit.target: Kall metodene i klassen bare med klarert.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Untrusted Data Security Risks](https://docs.com/rick-anderson-1/8710/untrusted-data-security-risks).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [uklarerte Data sikkerhetsrisiko](https://docs.com/rick-anderson-1/8710/untrusted-data-security-risks).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"></xref> class for the specified stream.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"> </xref> klasse for den angitte strømmen.

trans-unit.source: The ResourceReader constructor instantiates a <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> object that retrieves resources either from a standalone .resources file or from a .resources file that is embedded in an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren ResourceReader starter en <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>objektet som henter ressurser enten fra en frittstående .resources fil eller fra en .resources filen som er innebygd i en samling.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>

trans-unit.source: To read from a standalone .resources file, instantiate a <xref:System.IO.Stream> object and pass it to the ResourceReader constructor.
trans-unit.target: For å lese fra en frittstående .resources-fil, kan du starte en <xref:System.IO.Stream>objekt og sendes til konstruktøren ResourceReader.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: To read from an embedded .resources file, call the <xref:System.Reflection.Assembly.GetManifestResourceStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method with the case-sensitive name of the .resources file, and pass the returned <xref:System.IO.Stream> object to the ResourceReader constructor.
trans-unit.target: For å lese fra en innebygd .resources-fil, kan du kalle den <xref:System.Reflection.Assembly.GetManifestResourceStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden med skiller navnet .resources-filen, og pass det returnerte <xref:System.IO.Stream>objektet ResourceReader-konstruktøren.</xref:System.IO.Stream> </xref:System.Reflection.Assembly.GetManifestResourceStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Releases all operating system resources associated with this <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle operativsystemressurser som er knyttet til dette <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Close can be safely called multiple times.
trans-unit.target: Lukk kan bare kalles flere ganger.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den gjeldende forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When you are finished using this instance of <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>, call Dispose to release all resources used by this instance.
trans-unit.target: Når du er ferdig med denne forekomsten av <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>, kalle avhending for å frigi alle ressurser som brukes i denne forekomsten.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>

trans-unit.source: You should eliminate further references to this <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> instance so that the garbage collector can reclaim the memory of the instance instead of keeping it alive for finalization.
trans-unit.target: Du må fjerne flere referanser til denne <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>serverforekomsten slik at saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minne på forekomsten i stedet for å holde det aktivt for finalization.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>

trans-unit.source: Dispose calls the private Dispose(Boolean) method, which contains the code to release managed and unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Avhending kaller private Dispose(Boolean)-metoden, som inneholder koden for å frigi ressurser behandlet.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator for this <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en opplisting for denne <xref href="System.Resources.ResourceReader"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you enumerate resources by calling the GetEnumerator method and then repeatedly calling the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method on the returned <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator> object until the method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis liste ressurser ved å kalle metoden GetEnumerator og gjentatte ganger kaller den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>-metoden på den returnerte <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator>objekt til metoden returnerer `false`.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: The resource name is available from the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Key%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property; its value from the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Value%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Ressursnavnet er tilgjengelig fra den <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Key%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen; verdien fra det <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Value%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Value%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Key%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The example illustrates how to enumerate resources in this way.
trans-unit.target: Eksemplet viser hvordan du liste ressurser på denne måten.

trans-unit.source: The implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Value%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property by the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> class can throw the following exceptions: - <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException> The assembly that contains the type to which the data belongs cannot be found.
trans-unit.target: Implementeringen av den <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Value%2A?displayProperty=fullName>ved den <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>klassen kan throw følgende unntak:- <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException>Finner ikke samlingen som inneholder typen dataene tilhører.</xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException> </xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> </xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator.Value%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.FormatException> The data is not in the expected format.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.FormatException>Dataene er ikke i det forventede formatet.</xref:System.FormatException>

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.TypeLoadException> The type to which the data belongs cannot be found.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.TypeLoadException>Finner ikke typen dataene tilhører.</xref:System.TypeLoadException>

trans-unit.source: You can handle the exception by calling the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader.GetResourceData%2A> method to retrieve information about the data type and the byte array assigned to the named resource.
trans-unit.target: Du kan behandle unntaket ved å ringe det <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader.GetResourceData%2A>metode for å hente informasjon om datatypen og bytematrise tildelte navngitt.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader.GetResourceData%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "Retrieving Resources by Name with GetResourceData" section in the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> class topic.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, se "Henter ressurser av navnet med GetResourceData" i den <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>klassen emnet.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > The <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> class includes two methods that return enumerators.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Den <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>klassen inneholder to metoder som returnerer enumeratorene.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>

trans-unit.source: The GetEnumerator method returns an <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator> interface object and is the recommended method to call when enumerating resources.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEnumerator returnerer en <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator>grensesnittet objekt og metoden anbefalt å kalle når nummererer ressurser.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator>

trans-unit.target: Henter typenavn og data på en navngitt ressurs fra en åpen ressursfilen eller strømmen.

trans-unit.source: IEnumerable.GetEnumerator is an explicit interface implementation.
trans-unit.target: IEnumerable.GetEnumerator er implementering eksplisitt grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: It can be used only when the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Den kan brukes bare når den <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>forekomsten endres til en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader>

trans-unit.source: The recommended approach to enumerating the resources in a .resources file is to call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method of the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator> object returned by the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader.GetEnumerator%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Den anbefalte fremgangsmåten til opplisting av ressurser i en .resources-fil er å kalle den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator>objektet som ble returnert av den <xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader.GetEnumerator%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Resources.ResourceReader.GetEnumerator%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IDictionaryEnumerator> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>
